<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="<%= currentLang %>">
<head>
    <title><%= t("Privacy Policy") %> | <%= websiteName %></title>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>
</head>
<body>
<%- include('../partials/nav') %>

<main class="privacy-container">
    <h2 style="color: #F04A00;"><%= t("Privacy Policy") %></h2>

    <p><%= t("This privacy policy explains the data we collect when you use this site, and how we use that data.") %></p>
    <h3><%= t("Information We Collect") %></h3>
    <p><%= t("When you browse our site, we collect:") %></p>
    <ul>
        <li><%= t("Technical information, such as your browser, operating system, language preference, time of visit, and an anonymized network identifier are logged. The anonymized identifier is generated by hashing your IP address with a secret key to prevent reconstructing your original IP address.") %></li>
        <li><%= t("Usage information, such as which pages you viewed and the websites or search terms that referred you to the site") %></li>
    </ul>
    <p><%= t("If you contact us via email, we collect the name and email address you provide.") %></p>

    <h3><%= t("How We Use Information") %></h3>
    <p><%= t("When you browse our site, we collect data for security and monitoring purposes. This individual-level limited technical data about site visitors is deleted after 30 days. We may preserve aggregated technical information (e.g. browser type, operating system, and language preference) across all visitors to the site.") %></p>
    <p><%= t("If you contact us via email, the details you provide in your email are used solely to respond to your inquiry and are never shared or sold.") %></p>

    <h3><%= t("How We Share Information") %></h3>
    <p><%= t("We do not share or sell your data to any third parties.") %></p>

    <p>
        <%= t("If you have questions about this policy or your data, you may contact us at") %>
        <a href="mailto:<%= 'info@lotsarevacant.com' %>" style="color: #F04A00;">
            <%= 'info@lotsarevacant.com' %></a>.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 0.95em;">
        <%= t("Privacy policy last updated")%>: 2025-08-11
    </p>
</main>

<%- include('../partials/footer') %>
<script>
    window.TRANSLATIONS = <%- JSON.stringify(translationsForClient) %>;
    window.CURRENT_LANG = "<%= currentLang %>";
    function t(key) {
        return window.TRANSLATIONS[key] || key;
    }
</script>
<script src="js/mapNav.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
